00:49.766 --> 00:53.135
- Great. Now we have
to go to the car wash.

00:53.203 --> 00:55.204
- Oh, no.
I'm getting out here.

00:55.271 --> 00:56.672
What are you, crazy?

00:56.739 --> 00:59.741
You're on the side
of a freeway! It's dangerous!

00:59.809 --> 01:01.810
- Not as dangerous as
riding in that thing.

01:01.878 --> 01:03.812
Suit yourself.

01:10.720 --> 01:13.188
Am I clear?

01:13.256 --> 01:14.957
I'm going for it!

