11:44.820 --> 11:46.654
- ♪ and the silly thing
we learned ♪

11:46.722 --> 11:48.790
- ♪ is now they're friends ♪
- ♪ those plants are friends ♪

11:48.858 --> 11:50.725
- ♪ you like red,
